{"tid":223911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察「反搖控爆炸裝置」干擾成個空管系統","createTime":"2017-04-30T15:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T16:46:25.000Z","uid":5195,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"263cd87707f947f09421cb2bc6441688900470bd","tid":223911,"uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"#<br />\n公務員secret<br />\nCS2104<br />\n<br />\n(空管+警察) 你地班警察真係社會垃圾來<br />\n前排張德江來香港，今日印尼總統來香港<br />\n你哋架&quot;干涉搖控引爆炸彈&quot;既裝置，連空管頻道都干擾埋<br />\n香港成個空域所有飛機上人命就被你哋咁樣玩，全部frequency被你jam晒<br />\n我哋聽住你整出來ｄ巨響，完全俾唔到指示<br />\n彷彿個垃圾空管系統搞唔出人命，你哋就踩多一腳<br />\n仲有我哋成班空管員，戴住個headset耳都聾<br />\n打市民就叻，向天開槍搏升職就威，政要條命就係命，成天過萬賤民既命就唔係命<br />\n反正萬一撞飛機，幾百人死都告唔到警察誤殺，right?"},{"pid":"efd39f6aec6901b5ff7300c0ef5f5f5c2590ad65","tid":223911,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94684dff8677e64322ab4662c30ad3737636147d","tid":223911,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69084c687529fec1ebe7d7f74ae96a0faa052644","tid":223911,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"036577b88a9e33c4f336c6a4e293a1f49aba94a9","tid":223911,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccdb9b548e603e1becbafbae3f7ef7a891809a99","tid":223911,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"印尼依d 咁既國家總統，黎香港搞乜"},{"pid":"eb539733e6b84d3d82a9efa391cc3867584ff70d","