0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>車隊中，灰黑色的全頻無線電干擾車甚為觸目，翻查資料，全國人大委員長張德江去年（2016年）5月訪港時，此車亦有出動。現場所見，此車的車頂裝有十數支「天線」，相信用以干擾多種無線電波，例如遙控炸彈及遙控飛機等，以防止突發事件發生，同時，為免警方執勤受阻，某些無線電的頻譜並不會因此受干預。干擾車在記者面前經過時，記者的手機網絡一度中斷，相信受到該車干擾。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/551310/xlarge/9933aaeada2b9c5b937b38e9666c5180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F551310%2Fxlarge%2F9933aaeada2b9c5b937b38e9666c5180.jpg&h=e0ee5275&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n揸呢架車好快會生cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最好日日揸</blockquote><br />\n坐正天線下邊唔會有事，天線射唔到正下方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個訊號係球狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1105889614ef32f673b7689423cce0ac87243cc6","tid":223911,"uid":112813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:42:08.000Z","msg":"呢架車加埋個新空管系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雷達又唔work無線電又唔work <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67421bb93c528a9277e7cbd055b2927daeab5ffa","tid":223911,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>正常係用shielding策略，香港人整體工程學知識貧乏，死症，冇得救</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點做shielding 搵個大鐵鑊包住總統？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔可行就要諗第二樣，但如果係室內活動，無人機已經入唔到，預先亦應該守過晒冇炸彈，根本再冇必要用jammer"},{"pid":"69964d35370d94ab5e5bd41cce336f692841d7c0","tid":223911,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T04:01:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正常係用shielding策略，香港人整體工程學知識貧乏，死症，冇得救</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class